<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> فَلْيَتَحَرَّ الصَّوَابَ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>